'''''The Gift''''' is an [[Australia]]n observational [[Documentary film|documentary]] television program that aired on the [[Nine Network]] at {{nowrap|9:30 pm}}, Thursdays. It was narrated by ''[[60 Minutes (Australian TV program)|60 Minutes]]'' journalist [[Tara Brown]]. ''The Gift'' explores the stories and importance of organ donation in Australia. A second series aired at 9:00pm Wednesdays, debuting on 12 August 2009.
